GlassNav-GlassHole plugin
=========================

Authors
-------

* Ben Harlett (benharlett@gmail.com) — GlassHole integration, full-screen
  turn-by-turn HUD, speedometer overlay, share-from-Google-Maps pipeline,
  GlassHole BT bridge wiring.

Originally inspired by
----------------------

* GlassNav by CatotheCat11
  Repository: https://github.com/CatotheCat11/GlassNav
  Licensed under GPL-3.0-or-later.

  This module is a re-implementation in the spirit of GlassNav, designed
  to integrate with GlassHole's existing phone↔glass Bluetooth bridge.
  It uses the same GPL-3.0-or-later license as the original project so
  the upstream community can freely share improvements and contributions
  between the two codebases. No source files from the original
  GlassNav repository are imported verbatim — the UI flow, gesture
  vocabulary, and Bluetooth-location-streaming concept are credited
  here as inspiration.
